channel.title: Webclient PI Help me please xD
channel.description:
Hey everone may this sound realy dumb but i just started with using PI bases and ive downloaded a good sourch and a client. My client downloads the cache Automaticly from a direct downloading site. Thats fine. But I wanted to make a PI webclient. Everthing is already done in the client im pretty sure. (CacheDownloader.java, Signlink done, Client.java done etc) it also has one jarred file in the client that is named "client"
If i place the HTML code into my page it wont work. Im pretty sure i forgot something but cant find anything in all those PI webclient tuts.. (May something with the jarred client idk)
Hope you can help me :S
Thank you. YouriDudock
